data.text:
Jason Maxiell - Points

Jason Maxiell scores a career high 34 points (2015)

On December 18, 2015, Jason Maxiell set his career high in points in a China - CBA game. That day he scored 34 points in Tianjin's road win against Guangzhou, 116-122. He also had 11 rebounds, 3 assists, 1 steal and 3 blocks. He shot 15/23 from two, 0/1 from three, shooting at 62.5% from the field. He also shot 4/10 from the free-throw line.

Jason Maxiell - Rebounds

Jason Maxiell grabs a career high 23 rebounds (2015)

On December 27, 2015, Jason Maxiell set his career high in rebounds in a China - CBA game. That day he grabbed 23 rebounds in Tianjin's home loss against Shandong, 112-113. He also had 24 points, 5 assists, 1 steal and 2 blocks.

Jason Maxiell - Assists

Jason Maxiell gives a career high 5 assists (2007)

On November 14, 2007, Jason Maxiell tied his career high in assists in a NBA game. That day he dished 5 assists in Detroit's road win against Golden State, 104-111. He also had 14 points, 14 rebounds, 1 steal and 3 blocks.

Jason Maxiell - Steals

Jason Maxiell has a career high 3 steals (2008)

On November 30, 2008, Jason Maxiell tied his career high in steals in a NBA game. That day he reached 3 steals in Detroit's home loss against Portland, 85-96. He also had 4 points, 2 rebounds and 1 assist.

Jason Maxiell - Blocks

Jason Maxiell blocks a career high 8 shots (2005)

On January 29, 2005, Jason Maxiell set his career high in blocks in a NCAA game. That day he went for 8 blocks in Cincinnati Bearcats's home win against Houston Cougars, 87-68. He also had 14 points, 10 rebounds and 2 assists.
